Class Section

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hpsf.Section

  • public class Section
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a section in a PropertySet.(代表Property Set中的一个部分。)

        Constructs a Section by doing a deep copy of an existing Section. All nested Property instances, will be their mutable counterparts in the new MutableSection.(通过对现有节进行深度复制来构建节。所有嵌套的Property实例都将成为新MutableSection中的可变实例。)

               int offset)
        throws java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException
        Creates a Section instance from a byte array.(从字节数组创建Section实例。)
        Parameters:
        src - Contains the complete property set stream.(src -包含完整的属性集流。)
        offset - The position in the stream that points to the section's format ID.(Offset -流中指向部分格式ID的位置。)
        Throws:
        java.io.UnsupportedEncodingException - if the section's codepage is not supported.(java.io. UnspectedEnCodingResponse-如果不支持该部分的代码页。)

    • Method Detail

      • getFormatID

        public ClassID getFormatID()
        Returns the format ID. The format ID is the "type" of the section. For example, if the format ID of the first Section contains the bytes specified by org.apache.poi.hpsf.wellknown.SectionIDMap.SUMMARY_INFORMATION_ID the section (and thus the property set) is a SummaryInformation.(返回格式ID。格式ID是部分的“类型”。例如，如果第一个部分的格式ID包含org.apache.poi.hpsf.wellknown.SectionIDMap. SUMUS_INFORMATION_ID指定的字节，则该部分（以及属性集）是SummaryInfo。)
        Returns:
        The format ID(的格式ID)

      • setProperty

        public void setProperty(int id,
                        long variantType,
                        java.lang.Object value)
        Sets the value and the variant type of the property with the specified ID. If a property with this ID is not yet present in the section, it will be added. An already present property with the specified ID will be overwritten. A default mapping will be used to choose the property's type.(设置具有指定ID的属性的值和变体类型。如果具有此ID的属性尚未出现在部分中，则将添加它。具有指定ID的已经存在的属性将被覆盖。将使用默认映射来选择属性的类型。)
        Parameters:
        id - The property's ID.(id -房产的ID。)
        variantType - The property's variant type.(VariantType -属性的变体类型。)
        value - The property's value.(价值-房产的价值。)

      • wasNull

        public boolean wasNull()
        Checks whether the property which the last call to getPropertyIntValue(long) or getProperty(long) tried to access was available or not. This information might be important for callers of getPropertyIntValue(long) since the latter returns 0 if the property does not exist. Using wasNull the caller can distiguish this case from a property's real value of 0.(检查上次调用getPropertyIntValue（long）或getProperty（long）尝试访问的属性是否可用。此信息对于getPropertyIntValue（long）的调用者可能很重要，因为如果属性不存在，后者将返回0。使用wasbitt，调用者可以将此情况与属性的实际值0区分开来。)
        Returns:
        true if the last call to getPropertyIntValue(long) or getProperty(long) tried to access a property that was not available, else false.(如果对getPropertyIntValue（long）或getProperty（long）的最后一次调用试图访问不可用的属性，则为true，否则为true。)

      • getPIDString

        public java.lang.String getPIDString(long pid)
        Returns the PID string associated with a property ID. The ID is first looked up in the Sections private dictionary. If it is not found there, the property PID string is taken from sections format IDs namespace. If the PID is also undefined there, i.e. it is not well-known, "[undefined]" is returned.(返回与属性ID关联的ID字符串。首先在Sections私有字典中查找ID。如果在那里找不到它，则从格式ID部分命名空间中取出属性ID字符串。如果那里也未定义，即它不为人所知，则返回“[undefined]”。)
        Parameters:
        pid - The property ID(pid -属性ID)
        Returns:
        The well-known property ID string associated with the property ID pid(与属性ID pid关联的已知属性ID字符串)

      • equals

        public boolean equals(java.lang.Object o)
        Checks whether this section is equal to another object. The result is false if one of the the following conditions holds:
        • The other object is not a Section.
        • The format IDs of the two sections are not equal.
        • The sections have a different number of properties. However, properties with ID 1 (codepage) are not counted.
        • The other object is not a Section.
        • The properties have different values. The order of the properties is irrelevant.
        (检查此部分是否等于另一个对象。如果满足以下条件之一，则结果为假：另一个对象不是小节。两个部分的格式ID不相等。这些部分具有不同数量的属性。但是，ID为1（代码页）的属性不计算在内。另一个对象不是小节。这些属性具有不同的价值。属性的顺序无关紧要。)
        Overrides:
        equals in class java.lang.Object
        Parameters:
        o - The object to compare this section with(o -与此部分进行比较的对象)
        Returns:
        true if the objects are equal, false if not(如果对象相等，则为真，否则为假)

      • write

        public int write(java.io.OutputStream out)
          throws WritingNotSupportedException,
                 java.io.IOException
        Writes this section into an output stream.

        Internally this is done by writing into three byte array output streams: one for the properties, one for the property list and one for the section as such. The two former are appended to the latter when they have received all their data.

        (将此部分写入输出流。在内部，这是通过写入三个字节数组输出流来完成的：一个用于属性，一个用于属性列表，另一个用于部分本身。当前者收到所有数据时，两者将附加到后者上。)
        Parameters:
        out - The stream to write into.(out -要写入的流。)
        Returns:
        The number of bytes written, i.e. the section's size.(写入的字节数，即部分的大小。)
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs(java.io. IOResponse-如果发生I/O错误)
        WritingNotSupportedException - if HPSF does not yet support writing a property's variant type.(如果HPSF还不支持写入属性的变量类型，则抛出ExceptionNotSupportedException。)

      • setDictionary

        public void setDictionary(java.util.Map<java.lang.Long,java.lang.String> dictionary)
                   throws IllegalPropertySetDataException
        Sets the section's dictionary. All keys in the dictionary must be Long instances, all values must be Strings. This method overwrites the properties with IDs 0 and 1 since they are reserved for the dictionary and the dictionary's codepage. Setting these properties explicitly might have surprising effects. An application should never do this but always use this method.(设置该部分的字典。字典中的所有键必须是Long实例，所有值必须是String。此方法覆盖ID为0和1的属性，因为它们是为字典和字典的代码页保留的。显式设置这些属性可能会产生令人惊讶的效果。应用程序永远不应该这样做，而是始终使用此方法。)
        Parameters:
        dictionary - The dictionary(词典-词典)
        Throws:
        IllegalPropertySetDataException - if the dictionary's key and value types are not correct.(IllegalPropertySetDataResponse-如果字典的键和值类型不正确。)
        See Also:
        getDictionary()

      • getDictionary

        public java.util.Map<java.lang.Long,java.lang.String> getDictionary()
        Gets the section's dictionary. A dictionary allows an application to use human-readable property names instead of numeric property IDs. It contains mappings from property IDs to their associated string values. The dictionary is stored as the property with ID 0. The codepage for the strings in the dictionary is defined by property with ID 1.(获取该部分的字典。字典允许应用程序使用人类可读的属性名称，而不是数字属性ID。它包含从属性ID到其关联字符串值的映射。字典存储为ID为0的属性。字典中字符串的代码页由ID为1的属性定义。)
        Returns:
        the dictionary or null if the section does not have a dictionary.(如果该部分没有字典，则为字典或空。)
